<h4 id="indicator-function">Indicator function</h4>
<ol>
  <li>Indicator function of a convex set. Let $ C \subseteq \mathbf{R}^{n} $ be a
convex set, and consider the function $\mathbf{I_C}$ with domain C and
$I_C(x) = 0$ for all $x \in C$.
    <ul>
      <li>Itâ€™s extended-value extension is given by</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ol>

<p>\begin{equation}
\tilde{I}_{C}(x)=\left{\begin{array}{ll}0 &amp; x \in C \ \infty &amp; x \notin
C\end{array}\right.
\end{equation}</p>
